; AutoCAD Script File - Drawing Validation  
; Comprehensive drawing health check and validation

; Start with audit and fix
AUDIT _Y

; Check for and fix common issues
OVERKILL _ALL 0.001 _Y _Y _Y _Y _Y _Y

; Remove zero-length objects
DELCONSTR _ALL

; Check coordinate system
UCS _W

; Zoom to drawing extents to verify content
ZOOM _E

; Purge everything unused
-PURGE _A * _N
-PURGE _A * _N

; Verify no infinite coordinates
ZOOM _A

; Reset view
ZOOM _E

; Save validated drawing  
QSAVE